dataTable.scenarioOutline:
Given a user wants to login to Cura Health Care
When the user clicks the Menu tab
And clicks the Login tab
And enters "<Username>" , "<Password>"
And clicks the LOGIN button
And the user selects Facility
And selects the Healthcare Program
And selects the date value in Visit Date field
Then clicks Book Appointment button
And the appointment is made
